{"tid":1486421,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"巴黎有市民不滿餐廳上菜太慢 開槍擊斃侍應","createTime":"2019-08-19T01:03:57.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-19T10:56:25.000Z","uid":133680,"like":1,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"46d344aefb7cb62432bb9bd969d51f5c29d5de4e","tid":1486421,"uid":133680,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-19T01:03:57.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://m.mingpao.com/ins/%E5%9C%8B%E9%9A%9B/article/20190818/s00005/1566117505860/%E4%B8%8D%E6%BB%BF%E9%A3%9F%E7%89%A9%E9%81%B2%E9%81%B2%E6%9C%AA%E5%88%B0-%E5%B7%B4%E9%BB%8E%E9%A4%90%E5%BB%B3%E9%A3%9F%E5%AE%A2%E9%96%8B%E6%A7%8D%E6%89%93%E6%AD%BB%E4%BE%8D%E6%87%89\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F%25E5%259C%258B%25E9%259A%259B%2Farticle%2F20190818%2Fs00005%2F1566117505860%2F%25E4%25B8%258D%25E6%25BB%25BF%25E9%25A3%259F%25E7%2589%25A9%25E9%2581%25B2%25E9%2581%25B2%25E6%259C%25AA%25E5%2588%25B0-%25E5%25B7%25B4%25E9%25BB%258E%25E9%25A4%2590%25E5%25BB%25B3%25E9%25A3%259F%25E5%25AE%25A2%25E9%2596%258B%25E6%25A7%258D%25E6%2589%2593%25E6%25AD%25BB%25E4%25BE%258D%25E6%2587%2589&d=L%2B62T2%2Bn9M6BECqB4mLSssjT01h1KCp2%2Bw2KB0oDRGE%3D&h=61d40647\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F%25E5%259C%258B%25E9%259A%259B%2Farticle%2F20190818%2Fs00005%2F1566117505860%2F%25E4%25B8%258D%25E6%25BB%25BF%25E9%25A3%259F%25E7%2589%25A9%25E9%2581%25B2%25E9%2581%25B2%25E6%259C%25AA%25E5%2588%25B0-%25E5%25B7%25B4%25E9%25BB%258E%25E9%25A4%2590%25E5%25BB%25B3%25E9%25A3%259F%25E5%25AE%25A2%25E9%2596%258B%25E6%25A7%258D%25E6%2589%2593%25E6%25AD%25BB%25E4%25BE%258D%25E6%2587%2589&h=4a032c64\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://m.mingpao.com/ins/%E5%9C%8B%E9%9A%9B/article/20190818/s00005/1566117505860/%E4%B8%8D%E6%BB%BF%E9%A3%9F%E7%89%A9%E9%81%B2%E9%81%B2%E6%9C%AA%E5%88%B0-%E5%B7%B4%E9%BB%8E%E9%A4%90%E5%BB%B3%E9%A3%9F%E5%AE%A2%E9%96%8B%E6%A7%8D%E6%89%93%E6%AD%BB%E4%BE%8D%E6%87%89</a><br />\n<br />\n發生槍擊案的餐應售賣薄餅和三文治，有其他侍應指疑兇因為不滿食物的準備時間太長並失去耐性，故向侍應開槍。該侍應肩膀位置中槍，救護員到場為他急救，但最終當場傷重不治。<br />\n<br />\n槍擊案令當地居民和商戶大為震驚，一名29歲女子向當地傳媒表示，事發店舖是一間寧靜的餐廳，數月前才開業。另有居民稱當地最近涉及販毒和醉酒鬧事的罪案有上升趨勢。<br />\n<br />\n（BBC）"},{"pid":"546aa733a116830e74e0eaf1be7279a301b6275c","tid":1486421,"uid":257422,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-19T01:04:23.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://g2.dcdn.lt/images/pix/baltijos-kelias-v-cepliausko-nuotr-65429744.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fg2.dcdn.lt%2Fimages%2Fpix%2Fbaltijos-kelias-v-cepliausko-nuotr-65429744.jpg&h=6678ec11&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">8月23日 人鏈：香港之路Hong Kong Way正！式！上！線！！！！</span></span><br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1486119\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1486119</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n正式名稱：香港之路 The Hong Kong Way<br />\n日期：２０１９年８月２３日（星期五）<br />\n集合地點：港島線及荃灣觀塘線沿線各港鐵站<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n路線圖 (細節待定)<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/SOnPTuT.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FSOnPTuT.jpg&h=f65321a6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n大致分三段：<br />\n港島線（筲箕灣 &mdash; 堅尼地城）：13KM<br />\n荃灣線（黃埔 &mdash; 美孚）：7.02KM<br />\n觀塘線（深水埗 &mdash; 油塘）：12.6KM<br />\n<br />\n時序：<br />\n集合並在行人路上排隊 19:15-20:00<br />\n手牽手組人鏈 20:00-21:00<br />\n和平散去 21:00<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: limegreen;\">快啲幫手開post宣傳<br />\n 整文宣！！！！</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance.gif